{"type":"message","id":"537d659e","parentId":"7d1e82b2","timestamp":"2026-03-04T19:19:47.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The exec command needs approval. Let me try a different approach - I can use the message tool to get info about what's needed, or just ask the user to approve it.\n\nActually, wait - I'm being asked to help setup a Telegram channel. This seems like it could be:\n1. A Telegram supergroup/channel that the user wants to manage via OpenClaw\n2. Or they want to add this channel to their OpenClaw configuration\n\nLet me ask what they need help with specifically, since \"setup\" is pretty vague.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"I need a bit more detail — what does \"setup\" mean for channel -1003812821838?\n\n- Add it to OpenClaw for receiving/responding to messages?\n- Configure something specific (commands, filters, etc.)?\n- Something else?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"minimax/minimax-m2.5:free","usage":{"input":64,"output":164,"cacheRead":13062,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13290,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772651982667}}
